  "description": "8 New Dimensions ♦ 115+ New Mobs/Bosses ♦ Hundreds of New Blocks and Items ♦ Unique Weapons and Armor",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/site%20media/logo.png?raw=true\" alt=\"header\" width=\"1002\" height=\"282\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/site%20media/dimensions.png?raw=true\" alt=\"dimensions\" width=\"800\" height=\"220\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DivineRPG offers multiple Dimensions worth of content for you to explore.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Find the secrets that lie within</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/site%20media/bosses.png?raw=true\" alt=\"bosses\" width=\"800\" height=\"220\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DivineRPG has many bosses for you to battle.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Can you beat them all?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/site%20media/npc.png?raw=true\" alt=\"npcs\" width=\"800\" height=\"220\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Not every mob inside of DivineRPG is trying to kill you. Some mobs want to trade with you</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/site%20media/armory.png?raw=true\" alt=\"armory\" width=\"800\" height=\"220\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DivineRPG has lots of new armor, tools and weapons, each with different perks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">What will you choose?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">📺 Video FAQ Series</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We&rsquo;ve put together a helpful YouTube playlist to answer common questions and showcase DivineRPG's features in action.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEdW8z1ET4BKT87EOIGn1CVUg95bI8tt_&amp;si=msjYE_qnYe8K5YeU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>▶ Click here to view the full DivineRPG FAQ Playlist</strong></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold; color: #c0392b;\">⚠ Episode 6 specifically demonstrates the brand-new portal system &ndash; don't miss it!</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CdgSHo6vG0A?si=Wabouo1ullUsbjJz\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold; color: #c0392b;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/btdKcbs\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/site%20media/discord.png?raw=true\" alt=\"discord\" width=\"1125\" height=\"158\" /></a></p>\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 1em 0;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you wish to join our Discord just click the banner above. If you have questions about DivineRPG, we have a channel for that as well</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><del><a href=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/credits.md\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://github.com/DivineRPG/DivineRPG-Assets/blob/main/site%20media/credits.png?raw=true\" alt=\"credits\" width=\"1002\" height=\"282\" /></a></del></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Click the picture above to see the credits</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
